      'The practical implementation challenge on active construction sites is positioning and durability. Cameras need to be on temporary structures, weatherproofed, and repositioned as the site develops. Modern construction-grade monitoring systems account for this — but the site safety manager needs to plan camera coverage as part of the site safety plan from the beginning, not retrofit it after the fact.',
